track_notes: Not so difficult walk, need good shoes. The last part is a easy climbing.

This wonderfull walk is a hight mountain one; it is no very hard if all is OK. Good WX good shoes good health, the best way is clockwise, so you start climbing not very hard and get down to the refuge for a local beer! Plenty room for the car at parking and enouth room on summit if you dont have vertigo for antenna setup, in case you dont want to bring HF stuff, you will be able to valide the summit with VHF FM
This is one of the many path to reach this summit. Its hight mountain, so take care about wx, shoes and stuff.

from le Boreon, to Cougourde, lac de Trecolpas, Pas des Ladres, the way back from le Pisset and La Mairis.
